ld. A road runs through the upper right corner.\" data-full-url=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.8/nature-above-02.jpg\" data-link=\"#\" /></figure></li></ul></figure>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\";}}', 'no');
